      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that shows outstanding care and preservation throughout. The exterior presents beautifully with excellent paint, clean trim, and a highly detailed overall appearance, while the interior is equally impressive with minimal to no visible wear. This is the kind of car a buyer can feel confident showing, driving, and enjoying right away, with the fit, finish, and overall presentation expected from a top-tier vehicle. A standout example for anyone looking for one of the nicest ones available.",
