      "description": "$46,900 - This is a mint-condition used vehicle that presents exceptionally well and should satisfy a buyer looking for a clean, well-kept example. The exterior, interior, and overall presentation are in outstanding shape for a used car, with very minimal signs of wear and none of the obvious cosmetic or condition issues you would expect from an average pre-owned vehicle. It runs and drives as it should and gives the impression of having been very well cared for. If you\u2019ve been holding out for a particularly nice used vehicle rather than settling for an average one, this is the kind of car worth coming to see.",
